<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>For My Love 💗</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
background:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* HEADER */

header{
text-align:center;
padding:50px 20px;
background:#f793ce;
color:white;
font-size:34px;
font-weight:bold;
}

/* LOVE TIMER */

.timer{
text-align:center;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:20px;
color:#f793ce;
font-weight:bold;
}

/* LETTER */

.container{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:40px 20px;
}

.letter{
background:white;
border:4px solid #f793ce;
border-radius:20px;
padding:35px;
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.7;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
animation:fadeIn 2s ease;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);}
to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
}

/* GALLERY */

.gallery{
margin-top:60px;
}

.gallery h2{
text-align:center;
color:#f793ce;
}

.photos{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
gap:20px;
margin-top:30px;
}

.photos img{
width:100%;
border-radius:15px;
border:4px solid #f793ce;
transition:.3s;
}

.photos img:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

/* HEARTS */

.heart{
position:fixed;
bottom:-20px;
font-size:20px;
animation:floatUp 8s linear infinite;
color:#f793ce;
}

@keyframes floatUp{
from{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
to{transform:translateY(-120vh);opacity:0;}
}

/* POPUP */

.popup{
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
}

.popup-box{
background:white;
padding:40px;
border-radius:15px;
text-align:center;
border:3px solid #f793ce;
}

.popup button{
margin-top:15px;
padding:10px 20px;
border:none;
background:#f793ce;
color:white;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
}

footer{
text-align:center;
margin-top:40px;
padding:20px;
color:#888;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="popup" id="popup">
<div class="popup-box">
<h2>Hi Love 💗</h2>
<p>I made this little website for you.</p>
<button onclick="closePopup()">Open Letter</button>
</div>
</div>

<header>
Our Love Story 💗
</header>

<div class="timer" id="loveTimer"></div>

<div class="container">

<div class="letter">

<p>Hi Love, 9 months na ta together and I’m really happy na uyab tika. I love you always Love 💗. We’ve been through so much together already, and I’m willing to face whatever problems come as long as ikaw ang kauban nako.</p>

<p>Dli man kaayo ko goods sa words, but I always try to show my love through my actions as much as I can. During our OJT days, I’m so grateful we got to experience that time together. Always ko excited every morning pagmaabot ka. I loved the moments na magluto ka for us and sabay ta magbreakfast.</p>

<p>Then pag gabie na and muuli naka, medyo masad ko kay mulakaw naka and ako nalang mabilin. But I always think about the next morning again, na maabot ka and we get to spend time together.</p>

<p>I can’t wait for the day na magkauban na jud ta everyday and every night, living together and making more memories.</p>

<p>I don’t want anyone else, Love. Ikaw ra jud. I LOVE YOU SO MUCH AND ALWAYS NA LOVE 💗</p>

<p><strong>Only yours and yours only,<br>Love</strong></p>

</div>

<div class="gallery">

<h2>Our Memories 📸</h2>

<div class="photos">

<img src="photo1.jpg">
<img src="photo2.jpg">
<img src="photo3.jpg">
<img src="photo4.jpg">

</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>
Made with love 💗
</footer>

<script>

/* POPUP */

function closePopup(){
document.getElementById("popup").style.display="none";
}

/* HEARTS */

function createHeart(){
const heart=document.createElement("div");
heart.classList.add("heart");
heart.innerHTML="💗";
heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.fontSize=(15+Math.random()*25)+"px";

document.body.appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},8000)
}

setInterval(createHeart,500);

/* LOVE TIMER */

const startDate=new Date("June 13, 2025");

function updateTimer(){

const now=new Date();
const diff=now-startDate;

const days=Math.floor(diff/(1000*60*60*24));
const hours=Math.floor((diff/(1000*60*60))%24);
const minutes=Math.floor((diff/(1000*60))%60);

document.getElementById("loveTimer").innerHTML=
"Together for "+days+" days "+hours+" hours "+minutes+" minutes 💗";

}

setInterval(updateTimer,1000);

</script>

</body>
</html>
